      "id": "08661ef4_233e8dbc",
      "file_path": "integration-test/src/test/groovy/org/onap/cps/integration/performance/cps/DeltaPerfTest.groovy",
      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 107,
      "message": "I figured that there was no delta between anchors openroadm1 and openroadm2. So basically, we were applying zero delta hence such small times. \nSo I added a method to generate slightly modified anchor data, so that some delta is generated. Now we get some realistic numbers in all the tests",
